11:34.860 --> 11:36.896
Is that a wolf
masquerading as a dog?

11:38.070 --> 11:41.107
I sincerely hope
he isn't partial to human flesh.

11:41.320 --> 11:43.060
Only if ye're thickly bearded.

11:43.160 --> 11:45.526
Well, I shall take my chances.

11:46.410 --> 11:47.741
John Quincy Myers.

11:47.830 --> 11:48.865
Ian Murray.

11:49.080 --> 11:50.149
Pleased to meet you, Ian.

11:51.370 --> 11:53.827
A dalliance with a skunk
is no laughing matter, boy.

11:53.920 --> 11:54.909
Aye.

11:55.000 --> 11:57.662
But Mother Nature,
in all her bounty and wisdom,

11:57.760 --> 12:00.331
