reeking like the devil's arse.

12:10.270 --> 12:11.885
I've been allowing my beard to grow.

12:12.190 --> 12:14.852
Seems the men of the mountains
hereabouts have hearty ones.

12:14.940 --> 12:17.568
Uh, you've a long wait on yer hands.

12:17.650 --> 12:19.982
